sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor User as 用户
  participant UI as 移动端页面
  participant Repo as SQLite Repository
  participant Queue as sync_queue
  participant Engine as sync-engine
  participant Api as SyncController
  participant Sync as SyncService
  participant DB as PostgreSQL

  User->>UI: 离线新增 Todo / 记录能量
  UI->>Repo: 写入 local_todos / local_energy_entries
  Repo->>Queue: 追加 pending item(create/update/delete)
  Repo-->>UI: 本地立即可见

  UI->>Engine: syncNow(deviceId, lastPulledAt)
  Engine->>Queue: listPendingSyncItems(limit)
  Queue-->>Engine: pending items
  Engine->>Engine: 映射本地表到远端表名<br/>过滤不支持项
  Engine->>Api: POST /sync/push(items)
  Api->>Sync: pushChanges(userId, request)

  loop 每条变更
    Sync->>DB: 查找 / 创建 / 更新远端记录
    alt 服务端版本大于客户端版本
      DB-->>Sync: serverVersion
      Sync-->>Api: status=conflict
    else 写入成功
      DB-->>Sync: remoteId + newVersion
      Sync-->>Api: status=success
    else 写入失败
      Sync-->>Api: status=error
    end
  end

  Api-->>Engine: push results
  Engine->>Repo: success -> 更新 remote_id/version/sync_status
  Engine->>Queue: success -> 标记 synced
  Engine->>Queue: conflict/error -> 标记 failed 并保存错误

  Engine->>Api: POST /sync/pull(lastPulledAt)
  Api->>Sync: pullChanges(userId, request)
  Sync->>DB: 遍历同步表 updatedAt > lastPulledAt
  DB-->>Sync: changes
  Sync-->>Api: changes + pulledAt
  Api-->>Engine: pull response
  Engine-->>UI: SyncSummary(pushed, pulled, conflicts, errors)
